title: VLC.Media.Player+ 16 Skins
description:
VLC (initially VideoLAN Client) is a highly portable multimedia player for   
various audio and video formats (MPEG-1, MPEG-2, MPEG-4, DivX, mp3, ogg...) as
well as DVDs, VCDs, and various streaming protocols. It can also be used as a 
server to stream in unicast or multicast in IPv4 or IPv6 on a high-bandwidth 
network.                                                                     
will play just about everything
